ed its audit results&amp;nbsp;of nearly 40 firms with multiple&amp;nbsp;branch offices located throughout the United States.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;a data-cke-saved-href="http://In the meantime, you can have Bryan fill out this form and drop it into my secure file link. https://fincompliance.io/SendFiles/Index?p=db967e0f-115c-4c6a-9ef2-52d800adcf3c" href="http://In the meantime, you can have Bryan fill out this form and drop it into my secure file link. https://fincompliance.io/SendFiles/Index?p=db967e0f-115c-4c6a-9ef2-52d800adcf3c" target="_blank"&gt;View alert here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jlP1NFIqGx4/X8U4KO4Us2I/AAAAAAAAOcU/D69DDvS26eImaCLOw7_yjTG--YFMQW5mwCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/man-3653346_640.jpg" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="426" data-original-width="640" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-jlP1NFIqGx4/X8U4KO4Us2I/AAAAAAAAOcU/D69DDvS26eImaCLOw7_yjTG--YFMQW5mwCLcBGAsYHQ/s320/man-3653346_640.jpg" width="320" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Exam Focus/issues:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Compliance programs/supervision:&amp;nbsp; &lt;/strong&gt;During the audit, SEC examiners discovered issues related to: (1) firm procedures for custody, (2) advisor processes for&amp;nbsp;disclosing&amp;nbsp;fees, (3) overcharging clients, (4) non-compliance with advertising rules, and (4) inconsistencies with&amp;nbsp;Code of ethics reporting.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Investment Advice:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;In addition, OCIE staff noted deficiencies in: (1) advisor client&amp;nbsp;recommendations; (2) mutual fund share class disclosures; (3) setup of wrap fee programs, and (4) reporting of firm conflicts of interests.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;p style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-j7sUrfV3A9s/W6LcTi0Ph3I/AAAAAAAAJVg/Hwvm5f7Sb3EIGfAxG1f6i5pn_H82DWlIgCPcBGAYYCw/s1600/FINE%2BLOGO.png" style="background-color: white; clear: left; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;segoe ui web&amp;quot;, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="232" data-original-width="1600" height="28" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-j7sUrfV3A9s/W6LcTi0Ph3I/AAAAAAAAJVg/Hwvm5f7Sb3EIGfAxG1f6i5pn_H82DWlIgCPcBGAYYCw/s200/FINE%2BLOGO.png" width="200" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;b style="background-color: white; font-f