nt-size: 12px;"&gt;If the proposal passes, state-registered investment advisor&amp;nbsp;representatives (IAR's)&amp;nbsp;will have to comply with continuing education requirements or qualify for&amp;nbsp;a waiver.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a data-cke-saved-href="https://www.nasaa.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IAR-CE-Notice-and-Request-for-Comment-on-Amended-Model-Rule-100720.pdf" href="https://www.nasaa.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/IAR-CE-Notice-and-Request-for-Comment-on-Amended-Model-Rule-100720.pdf" style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;" target="_blank"&gt;More here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span face="verdana, geneva, sans-serif" style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;Send comments by email&amp;nbsp;to both NASAA (nasaacomments@nasaa.org) and Linda Cena (cenal@michigan.gov), Chair of the IAR CE Committee.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;span face="verdana,geneva,sans-serif"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12px;"&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZA7CXZZvoQk/X8U3Papo9sI/AAAAAAAAOcM/w49Lx9Tb3CAzjOJjGBcGb8CEpPTuiQ_BACLcBGAsYHQ/s640/phone-1052023_640.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="480" data-original-width="640" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZA7CXZZvoQk/X8U3Papo9sI/AAAAAAAAOcM/w49Lx9Tb3CAzjOJjGBcGb8CEpPTuiQ_BACLcBGAsYHQ/s320/phone-1052023_640.jpg" width="320" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"&gt;----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;spa