;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Ongoing/annual services.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Compliance Management&amp;nbsp;System:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Compliance portal for resources, forms, and checklists.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Business Management System:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Business portal for file sharing, e-contracts, and more.&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Advisor Continuity/Solicitor Support:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp; RIA Succession/continuity/solicitor services.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;b style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Business/Referral Network:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Inquire about advertising/consulting projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://fincompliance.io/brochure" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="450" data-original-width="375" height="200" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2zIqFsLJ5n0/XhTsyZDDDlI/AAAAAAAAMS0/nanGp54G5dQPOvvKdWCd-O2u4WTqH3UJQCLcBGAsYHQ/s200/FIN%2BCompliance%2BBrochure%2Bpg.%2B1%2B-%2BBlog.png" width="166" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; border: 1pt none; padding: 0in;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Our Approach&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;segoe ui web&amp;quot;, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&am