&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;April 20, 2020.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Super Account Administrators (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: mediumblue; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;SAAs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;) with more than one user and/or administrator account must login to&amp;nbsp;certify that individuals have&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;the right of access to FINRA systems&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;to perform related filing&amp;nbsp;responsibilities (e.g. ADV Part 1, 2, 3, U4, U5, ADV-W filings).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center;"&gt;Certification period is -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: red; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;April 20 - July 20, 2020&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align="center" style="margin: 0in; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5xvMalIJzNo/Xp5Zkzd_xyI/AAAAAAAANNA/kxeRsp9lM-ojBF-9Qv6ERL2C52hN0bXlQCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/042020%2B-%2BUser%2BCertification%2B-%2Bv1.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="329" data-original-width