4-21T16:38:36.007-07:00</updated><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='E-Contracts'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Secure File Sharing'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='FIN Compliance'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Compliance Management'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='Version 1.1'/><category scheme='http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#' term='FIN Lancer'/><title type='text'>Six Ways to Use FIN Lancer for Compliance &amp; Business Tasks</title><content type='html'>&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;By Cory Roberson, Principal of FIN Compliance, Lancer, Ventures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;By David McNeal, Contributor of My Compliance Blog&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="background: white; color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px;"&gt;April 7, 2020.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="background: white; color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px;"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="background: white; color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px;"&gt;FIN Lancer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;is&amp;nbsp;a tool&amp;nbsp;for firms to share documents, delegate tasks, send communications, and prepare e-contracts with&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;advisors, reps, consultants, staff, client, vendors, and&amp;nbsp;other investment advisors&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;"&gt;FIN Lancer is now integrated onto our compliance management dashboard at:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="http://fincompliance.io/" style="font-family: verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;"&gt;FINCompliance.io&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;"&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="color: red; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="color: red; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;Six&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt; ways to Use our Business Management Portal&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; line-height: 107%;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;1 - Share ADV Documents with your team via Project or Client Center.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: start;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px;"&gt;2 - Share sensitive files/folders with your compliance or operations staff.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;3 – Send annual ADV/public disclosure documents* via email or link (for non-secure/public records).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: start;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px;"&gt;4 - Enter your&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="http://paypal.me/"&gt;&lt;span style="color: blue;"&gt;Paypal.me&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;link to send invoices to vendors.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: start;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px;"&gt;5 - Access our E-Contracts plugin to send new or updated agreements to clients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; line-height: 107%;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: start;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;6 - Add your Profile to FIN Lancer Advisor Directory to connect w/ other firms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BnCVLwAFUoo/XoS_kK6-eaI/AAAAAAAANBc/3COzKYXry2sT0iSbRvbNOyoMs7kQclQ-QCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/Photo%2B-%2B14.png" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="523" data-original-width="1112" height="297" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BnCVLwAFUoo/XoS_kK6-eaI/AAAAAAAANBc/3COzKYXry2sT0iSbRvbNOyoMs7kQclQ-QCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/Photo%2B-%2B14.png" width="640" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px; letter-spacing: -0.333333px;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Tools/Systems uses in FIN Lancer include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;File Sharing to other system users&lt;/b&gt; &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;(compliance/operations staff)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;(sending docs to users w or w/o sensitive information)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Steps:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;1 - Create Folder Name in Client or Project Center&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;2 - Click on click on Black symbol (under tools)&amp;nbsp; to add a user&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;3 - See&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;add users&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;screen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;4 - Click on a Folder to add/view files&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;5 - Drag/Drop files from your desktop or directory&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Rbr_5vYMNzg/Xp9-eBdXpTI/AAAAAAAANQc/HjZXr7LYJOUFaNW5-huAKdNKqsV9CKDvwCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/Photo%2B-%2B1.png" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; display: inline !important; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="360" data-original-width="640" height="112" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Rbr_5vYMNzg/Xp9-eBdXpTI/AAAAAAAANQc/HjZXr7LYJOUFaNW5-huAKdNKqsV9CKDvwCLcBGAsYHQ/s200/Photo%2B-%2B1.png" width="200" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;File Sharing with links for public documents&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;(ADV/general disclosure documents)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;(sending docs via email w/ no sensitive information or encryption needed)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Steps:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;1 - Go to File Listings (Drag/Drop section)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;2 - Click on&amp;nbsp;to share open link with anyone (not secure)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Integrate your firm Paypal.me link&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;(billing vendors)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;(vendors/not for client billing)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Steps:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;1 - Go to Invoicing/Billing (Drag/Drop section)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;2 - Add Paypal.me link (see instructions or go to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.paypal.me/"&gt;https://www.paypal.me/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;3- Create invoice and send to vendors&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZalkbQk7eb0/Xp9-RjK-TkI/AAAAAAAANQU/tGPu-n1TV18AC7CXKdjmDdU1F4rmsBrxQCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/Photo%2B-%2B22%2B-%2BFIN%2BLancer%2B-%2BInvoice.png" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="495" data-original-width="701" height="140" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZalkbQk7eb0/Xp9-RjK-TkI/AAAAAAAANQU/tGPu-n1TV18AC7CXKdjmDdU1F4rmsBrxQCLcBGAsYHQ/s200/Photo%2B-%2B22%2B-%2BFIN%2BLancer%2B-%2BInvoice.png" width="200" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;