"mso-bookmark: _Hlk20078121;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;segoe ui web&amp;quot;, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 1.5pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;segoe ui web&amp;quot;, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: normal;"&gt;&lt;span style="mso-bookmark: _Hlk20078121;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Business Management -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="mso-bookmark: _Hlk20078121;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;We provide firms with task-management processes and a business directory to connect with other firms for continuity, succession planning, partnerships, and deal flow.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="mso-bookmark: _Hlk20078121;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Also, we have a small network of&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;referral partners&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;for practice management, operations workflows, accounting, and website design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="mso-bookmark: _Hlk20078121;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-color: whit