heir internal regulatory review programs.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;segoe ui web&amp;quot;, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 1.5pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;segoe ui web&amp;quot;, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 1.5pt;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Our product line consists of:&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;RIA Consults-Roberson Consults Group, a compliance consulting firm, RIA Review, a compliance-management system, B-D Review, a Hybrid-management system&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: red; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;(est. in 2020)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;*, and FIN Lancer, a Business/Task Management system.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align="center" style="background-color: white; font-family: &amp;quot;segoe ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;segoe ui web&amp;quot;, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; margin: 0in; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;b style="font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: 