ormal" style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Compliance Management&amp;nbsp;System:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Online portal.&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Business Management System:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Online portal.&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Advisor Transition Support:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp; RIA Matchmaking/continuity services.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;Business/Referral Network:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; padding: 0in;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Inquire about advertising/consulting projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: bla