on: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;We&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style="border: 1pt none; padding: 0in;"&gt;research regulatory updates&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;from state, SEC, and/or FINRA jurisdictions. We’re here to help as some rules/regulations may be amended over time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="mso-bookmark: _Hlk20078121;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align="center" style="font-size: 13.3333px; margin: 0in; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 1.5pt;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;About FIN Compliance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;FIN Compliance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;"&gt;&lt;a href="file:///C:/Users/coryh/Downloads/FINCompliance.io"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;FinCompliance.io&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;is a consortium of compliance, consulting, and business management solutions designed to help boutique investment firms to structure, maintain, and develop their internal regulatory review programs.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 1.5pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 13.3333px; line-height: normal; margin-bottom: 1.5pt;"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Our product line consists of:&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;RIA Consults-Roberson Consults Group, a compliance consulting firm, RIA Review, a compliance-management system, B-D Review, a Hybrid-management system&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: red; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;(est. in 2020)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;*, and FIN Lancer, a Business/Task Management system.&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align="center" style="font-size: 13.3333px; margin: 0in; text-align: center; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;b style="font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: black; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 1