ze: 10.0pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt; line-height: 115%;"&gt;The new platform will be integrated onto our compliance management platform for paid users located at: &lt;a href="http://fincompliance.io/"&gt;FINCompliance.io&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt; line-height: 115%;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Cwj7MKjU7eY/XoKhAVFXL1I/AAAAAAAAM8M/QSjUfMwcv40zUxkiKG44EpnlOfSXyG-YwCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/033020%2B-%2BFIN%2BLancer%2BDashboard%2B-%2Bv1.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="604" data-original-width="1327" height="289" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Cwj7MKjU7eY/XoKhAVFXL1I/AAAAAAAAM8M/QSjUfMwcv40zUxkiKG44EpnlOfSXyG-YwCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/033020%2B-%2BFIN%2BLancer%2BDashboard%2B-%2Bv1.png" width="640" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt; line-height: 115%;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="mso-spacerun: yes;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;div style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt; letter-spacing: -0.25pt; line-height: 115%;"&gt;Combining compliance resources with task management tools&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div sty