eir brand through enhancing digital marketing practices, &lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;improving business and technology processes, and navigating firm compliance requirements&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNoSpacing"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNoSpacing"&gt;&lt;span lang="EN" style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;Inquire to join us or &lt;i&gt;&lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;if your interested in a service(s).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="color: #212121; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-lSzx9eDBISU/XaI_H-7ZfrI/AAAAAAAALts/iggm61hGMpgC5RcwWQ7KyLZBELt6B1qVwCLcBGAsYHQ/s1600/121219%2B-%2BWIN%2BCollective.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="572" data-original-width="907" height="401" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-lSzx9eDBISU/XaI_H-7ZfrI/AAAAAAAALts/iggm61hGMpgC5RcwWQ7KyLZBELt6B1qVwCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/121219%2B-%2BWIN%2BCollective.png" width="640" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style="color: #212121; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="color: #212121; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;W.I.N Collective topics Include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="l