b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;Strategy -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Identify Business Goals &amp;amp; How To Reach Your Target Audience&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;Command -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Attention Through Relevant Vibrant Visuals&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;Engage -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;A Positive User Experience to Increase Goal Conversions&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; margin: 0in; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;Measure -&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;Data &amp;amp; The Key Factors to A Clients Success&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot