 tools to work smarter not harder.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-indent: -0.25in;"&gt;Their Email Campaigns have a low open and click rate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-indent: -0.25in;"&gt;They need design services that are cohesive with their brand.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-indent: -0.25in;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #212121; font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;For more information, visit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://elitevivant.com/" style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"&gt;https://eli