able by Q4 2019)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;Access all services on one site: &lt;a href="http://fincompliance.io/"&gt;FINCompliance.io&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif; font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&lt;a href="file:///C:/Users/coryh/Google%20Drive/All%20-%20Business%20Operations%20Center/Operations%20-%20Sales%20Partner%20Program%20Packets/FINCompliance.io"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: &amp;quot;verdana&amp;quot; , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13.3333px;"&gt;Review &lt;a href="https://documentcloud.adobe.com/link/track?uri=urn%3Aaaid%3Ascds%3AUS%3Af38d50d9-2983-4e9a-9820-b6a078bd6aeb"&gt;our brochure&lt;/a&gt; here&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hotDfYC-fEM/XdBrnTxQjAI/AAAAAAAAL_E/PVY91KXTLY08eb8XqiZxzBofE4ZMO_HeQCEwYBhgL/s1600/System%2BWorkflows%2B%252B%2BDirectory.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-original-height="372" data-original-width="501" height="296" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-hotDfYC-fEM/XdBrnTxQjAI/AAAAAAAAL_E/PVY91KXTLY08eb8XqiZxzBofE4ZMO_HeQCEwYBhgL/s400/System%2BWorkflows%2B%252B%2BDirectory.png" width="400" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: cen